Subject: Bridge Obstruction Morphology

Description: Non-proof research morphology for classifying recurring bridge failures across the seven math problems project.

& [BridgeObstructionMorphology] is a research inquiry tool
  + [tool_uuid] is 2631f405-7ff2-4a38-a490-587962ab9b2b
  + [project] is seven math problems
  + [created_at] is 2026-06-27
  + [source_synthesis] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\events\project_reflections\2026-06-26_heartbeat_reentry_cycle_synthesis_001.sop
  + [public_synthesis] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\seven_math_problems\Public_Research_State_Synthesis.sop
  + [role] is study the recurring form of failed proof bridges without claiming proof progress
  + [not_role] is solving any Millennium Problem, replacing theorem targets, or treating analogy as evidence

& [MorphologyColumnSet] is the bridge-failure surface
  + [lane] is the problem lane or model context
  + [local_structure] is the meaningful partial object or organized corridor already present
  + [bridge_type] is transfer, propagation, generation, simulation, validation, reconstruction, or model_boundary
  + [missing_bridge] is the named theorem, estimate, construction, or validation step not yet present
  + [authority_boundary] is proof_blocked, model_only, source_boundary, or accepted_external
  + [next_legitimate_motion] is theorem_target, validation_target, model_calibration, public_synthesis, source_boundary, or quiet_watch

& [CurrentMorphologyMap] is the six-lane bridge obstruction table
  + [bsd] is transfer morphology
    = local_structure: diagonal-cycle and triple-product source-count corridor
    = bridge_type: transfer
    = missing_bridge: source_transfer_to_target_mordell_weil_rank
    = authority_boundary: proof_blocked
    = next_legitimate_motion: theorem_target
  + [navier_stokes] is propagation_and_criterion morphology
    = local_structure: quadrupole pressure-work route, active balls, localized entropy pressure work, and tail module
